This paper is about developing a backpropagation algorithm for training second order neural networks, which are a type of artificial neural network. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also discusses the nonlinear modeling ability of second order neurons, which suggests a connection to sub-categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper mentions the implementation of fuzzy logic operations, which could relate to sub-categories such as cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
